        description: "$520(4 hours prepaid), people have stressed every day and the stresses are the silent killer, why donâ€™t you treat yourself well and relax your body and mind? You can share the membership card for your family members. Enjoy these SPECIAL Therapeutic Treatments to decrease the stresses and cleared your mind.",
        details: ""
